4.1 authentication: (http://bazaar.launchpad.net/~mysql/mysql-server/5.5/view/head:/sql/password.c)

  SERVER:  public_seed=create_random_string()
           send(public_seed)

  CLIENT:  recv(public_seed)
           hash_stage1=sha1("password")
